(Toothpaste, Sanitary Pads,
Detergent, Trash Bags)

74
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:41,640
Water.

75
00:03:45,290 --> 00:03:46,410
Are you serious?

76
00:03:46,410 --> 00:03:47,750
Do you have to write that down?

77
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:51,520
In this case, I don't need
to check my phone back and forth

78
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,050
so that it can last a few more days.

79
00:03:53,400 --> 00:03:54,520
I'm so impressed.

80
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:55,450
You're frugal with

81
