93
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:22,760
Yao,

94
00:04:22,770 --> 00:04:24,410
our team can get medals, right?

95
00:04:24,410 --> 00:04:25,970
I can participate in the relay, right?

96
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,160
Of course. Why would our coach

97
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,770
form a team that can't win a medal?

98
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:32,410
If I can compete at every stop...

99
00:04:33,170 --> 00:04:34,010
Yao,

100
00:04:34,360 --> 00:04:35,970
is the prize money
settled after each stop

101
00:04:36,330 --> 00:04:37,740
or after the championship is over?

102
00:04:38,270 --> 00:04:39,970
It's up to the finance department,

103
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:42,880
