105
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:45,840
Wait a minute.

106
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,730
(Speed Skates)
- Look. - What's this?

107
00:04:50,850 --> 00:04:52,240
My dream skates.

108
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:53,770
If everything goes well,

109
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,530
I can buy them

110
00:04:55,530 --> 00:04:57,240
after paying off my debt.

111
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:58,560
Brat,

112
00:04:58,650 --> 00:05:00,770
