113
00:05:00,970 --> 00:05:01,880
Don't they look good?

114
00:05:02,210 --> 00:05:03,360
Look at you.

115
00:05:05,650 --> 00:05:06,490
Lin Ge,

116
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,730
