125
00:05:40,210 --> 00:05:41,360
Behave yourself.

126
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:51,050
My hair is still wet.

127
00:05:54,290 --> 00:05:55,610
Me too.

128
00:05:56,210 --> 00:05:57,120
Let it be.

129
00:06:11,970 --> 00:06:13,680
I think she's injured.

130
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:19,320
It happens all the time.

131
00:06:19,650 --> 00:06:21,870
Pretend you didn't see it,
or you'll be doomed.

132
