138
00:06:44,410 --> 00:06:46,120
Not for me. It's for Zhu.

139
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,530
Put it back.

140
00:07:11,860 --> 00:07:12,700
Where's Lin Feng?

141
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:15,060
He's having a fever. 39 degrees.

142
00:07:15,420 --> 00:07:16,580
