162
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,080
Keep practicing.

163
00:07:58,620 --> 00:07:59,620
Now, move.

164
00:07:59,820 --> 00:08:00,660
Okay.

165
00:08:01,090 --> 00:08:01,950
- Let's go.
- Come on.

166
00:08:01,950 --> 00:08:02,860
- Come on.
- Let's go.

167
00:08:03,570 --> 00:08:04,410
Hurry.

168
00:08:12,700 --> 00:08:13,580
Start training.

169
00:08:32,660 --> 00:08:33,500
