173
00:08:41,460 --> 00:08:43,220
My assessment results
are better than Tian Yu's.

174
00:08:43,410 --> 00:08:44,700
Why can't I practice relay?

175
00:08:45,220 --> 00:08:47,100
It's not the same thing.

176
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:48,700
Her speed is slow

177
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:50,540
because of her core strength,

178
00:08:50,540 --> 00:08:51,460
which can be improved.

179
00:08:52,050 --> 00:08:54,700
You need to correct your movements.

180
00:08:54,700 --> 00:08:55,700
If you develop bad habits,

181
00:08:56,180 --> 00:08:57,620
you won't be able to

182
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:59,580
improve your speed anymore.

183
00:09:00,190 --> 00:09:01,030
But

184
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:03,460
it doesn't conflict with
the competition, does it?

185
00:09:05,220 --> 00:09:06,580
Why do you want to compete?

186
00:09:06,740 --> 00:09:07,580
Because...

187
00:09:09,280 --> 00:09:10,940
I want to win.

188
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:15,820
I told you to trust your coach.

189
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:16,940
It's only been a few days.

190
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,820
Did you forget it all?

191
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:27,620
It's time to train.

192
00:09:27,740 --> 00:09:28,940
Stop wasting time.

193
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:29,780
Just go.

194
00:09:31,940 --> 00:09:32,980
Thanks, coach.

195
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:55,940
Just put it here.

196
00:10:01,700 --> 00:10:02,580
Gather up.

197
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:05,020
Come on.

198
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:15,980
Newcomers, you've had
enough time to adjust,

199
00:10:16,140 --> 00:10:18,320
and I know each member's situation.

200
00:10:18,740 --> 00:10:19,740
From now on,

201
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:22,140
