by Songbei Provincial Team.

202
00:10:22,930 --> 00:10:25,100
However, don't get carried away.

203
00:10:25,700 --> 00:10:26,660
Listen carefully,

204
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,020
if you can't meet the standard,

205
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:30,540
you'll be kicked out immediately.

206
00:10:33,010 --> 00:10:35,130
Let's talk about the men's team.

207
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:37,980
Nie Chi, Fang Chao,

208
00:10:38,460 --> 00:10:40,460
do tactical simulations with the seniors.

209
00:10:44,420 --> 00:10:45,460
