210
00:10:45,740 --> 00:10:46,580
No.

211
00:10:47,660 --> 00:10:48,780
I've been trained

212
00:10:48,900 --> 00:10:50,420
but never competed in a real race.

213
00:10:53,660 --> 00:10:55,320
