- and you can rest.

592
00:28:31,860 --> 00:28:33,820
You can also enjoy the view.

593
00:28:34,420 --> 00:28:35,620
I just want to ride alone.

594
00:28:37,340 --> 00:28:39,140
Zhu, why don't we share a bike?

595
00:28:39,380 --> 00:28:40,380
Wait, what are you doing?

596
00:28:40,660 --> 00:28:42,340
Han, you can ride with Nie Chi.

597
00:28:42,900 --> 00:28:44,420
We're both men.

598
00:28:44,540 --> 00:28:45,420
It's awkward.

599
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:47,340
Don't forget your promise.

600
00:28:49,660 --> 00:28:50,500
Thanks.

601
00:28:57,100 --> 00:28:59,260
What's going on?

602
00:29:01,340 --> 00:29:03,260
It seems you got

603
00:29:03,340 --> 00:29:04,970
carried away.

604
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:07,370
Everybody.

605
00:29:07,860 --> 00:29:08,980
Let's race!

606
00:29:08,980 --> 00:29:10,540
Fine. Bring it on.

607
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:11,580
Come on!

608
00:29:26,170 --> 00:29:28,780
♪Living an ordinary life is not giving up♪

609
00:29:29,620 --> 00:29:31,100
I passed you.

610
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:33,660
I'm back.

611
00:29:34,020 --> 00:29:35,580
Bye, guys.

612
00:29:36,030 --> 00:29:41,470
♪Make every day meaningful♪

613
00:29:42,850 --> 00:29:45,310
♪I just want to be an ordinary person♪

614
00:29:46,270 --> 00:29:49,360
♪Always grateful,
not owing anything to anyone♪

615
00:29:49,740 --> 00:29:52,520
♪Openly daring to love and hate♪

616
00:29:54,820 --> 00:29:55,660
You...

617
00:29:56,610 --> 00:29:58,580
♪I just want to be an ordinary person♪

618
00:29:58,590 --> 00:29:59,900
You're playing dirty!

619
00:30:01,340 --> 00:30:03,260
No rabbit can beat

620
00:30:03,540 --> 00:30:05,260
a turtle with wheels.

621
00:30:06,810 --> 00:30:11,810
♪Take off the mask and run freely♪

622
00:30:17,100 --> 00:30:18,420
Yes. Nice pose.

623
00:30:18,820 --> 00:30:20,420
Keep it. That's great.

624
00:30:21,380 --> 00:30:22,220
Okay.

625
00:30:23,580 --> 00:30:25,660
His eyes are about to pop out.

626
00:30:25,820 --> 00:30:26,660
What?

627
00:30:27,980 --> 00:30:30,580
Look at the way Nie Chi looks at Lin Ge.

628
00:30:31,820 --> 00:30:34,100
You can't hide your feelings
when looking at someone you like.

629
00:30:35,660 --> 00:30:37,100
Why don't you look at me more often?

630
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:38,860
Reflect on yourself.

631
00:30:38,860 --> 00:30:39,700
Wait.

632
00:30:40,540 --> 00:30:41,380
Look.

633
00:30:41,860 --> 00:30:44,060
Zhu is more suspicious.

634
00:30:44,580 --> 00:30:46,100
She's staring at Nie Chi.

635
00:30:48,300 --> 00:30:49,180
No way.

636
00:30:49,180 --> 00:30:50,500
I've known her for a long time,

637
00:30:50,500 --> 00:30:52,540
and she's never stared at anyone.

638
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:53,740
You have poor insight.

639
00:30:54,860 --> 00:30:56,020
So, I fell in love with you.

640
00:30:56,580 --> 00:30:58,300
Are you serious?

641
00:30:58,300 --> 00:31:00,180
- What do you mean?
- Enough. I'm sorry.

642
00:31:00,320 --> 00:31:01,340
I'm sorry.

643
00:31:13,420 --> 00:31:14,260
Like this.

644
00:31:14,340 --> 00:31:15,780
Take a good picture of me.

645
00:31:17,580 --> 00:31:18,580
Get more meat.

646
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:21,300
No need. My meat is cooked.

647
00:31:21,380 --> 00:31:22,220
Cooked?

648
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,490
Give it to me.

649
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:24,380
It's for Lin Ge.

650
00:31:24,390 --> 00:31:25,320
Don't waste time.

651
00:31:25,330 --> 00:31:26,420
I'll give it to Zhu.

652
00:31:32,340 --> 00:31:33,380
Come on. Have a bite.

653
00:31:34,100 --> 00:31:34,980
No.

654
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:36,420
Nie Chi just made it.

655
00:31:36,580 --> 00:31:37,580
He wanted to keep it.

656
00:31:37,900 --> 00:31:38,820
You must be hungry,

657
00:31:38,820 --> 00:31:40,060
so I grabbed it over for you.

658
00:31:42,540 --> 00:31:43,380
Thanks.

659
00:31:48,340 --> 00:31:49,180
How is it?

660
00:32:01,100 --> 00:32:02,100
Nie Chi.

661
00:32:02,420 --> 00:32:03,380
What the hell is that?

662
00:32:03,820 --> 00:32:05,500
Try it. Do you think it's edible?

663
00:32:06,020 --> 00:32:06,860
What?

664
00:32:11,060 --> 00:32:11,900
How is it?

665
00:32:12,540 --> 00:32:13,380
It's good.

666
00:32:13,740 --> 00:32:14,900
Just a bit salty.

667
00:32:15,420 --> 00:32:16,620
Is the salt free?

668
00:32:16,620 --> 00:32:17,620
Stop doing this.

669
00:32:18,580 --> 00:32:20,340
Less salt, more caring.

670
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:21,820
I can't let Zhu down

671
00:32:21,820 --> 00:32:23,380
again.

672
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:24,980
I didn't ask you to do that.

673
00:32:25,380 --> 00:32:26,340
It was for Lin Ge.

674
00:32:27,300 --> 00:32:28,820
Why didn't you tell me it was cooked?

675
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:31,380
Why are you so stingy?

676
00:32:39,540 --> 00:32:40,860
Does it taste a little...?

677
00:32:40,860 --> 00:32:41,820
It's bland.

678
00:32:43,180 --> 00:32:44,020
Add more salt.

679
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:46,820
Let me try.

680
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:48,900
It's for Fang Chao.

681
00:32:49,200 --> 00:32:50,340
I'm hungry. Just one bite.

682
00:32:50,340 --> 00:32:52,180
No, wait a minute. Go.

683
00:32:52,820 --> 00:32:54,860
Nie, you're too good to me.

684
00:32:55,300 --> 00:32:56,260
Fang Chao!

685
00:32:57,340 --> 00:32:58,420
I'll grill your favorite

686
00:32:58,420 --> 00:32:59,580
chicken wings.

687
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:06,580
Rock, paper, scissors.

688
00:33:08,340 --> 00:33:09,820
What are the odds?

689
00:33:10,060 --> 00:33:11,980
Just pick. Dare or Dare?

690
00:33:12,300 --> 00:33:14,260
Dare or Dare?

691
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:15,220
Only Dare?

692
00:33:15,900 --> 00:33:16,850
You can sing a song.

693
00:33:16,870 --> 00:33:17,900
The one you're good at.

694
00:33:17,900 --> 00:33:19,140
Yes. Sing a song.

695
00:33:19,140 --> 00:33:19,980
No.

696
00:33:20,780 --> 00:33:22,380
When I chose Dare,

697
00:33:22,380 --> 00:33:24,180
you asked me to imitate a gorilla.

698
00:33:24,380 --> 00:33:26,060
How can you ask him to sing?

699
00:33:26,260 --> 00:33:28,060
I can't accept it.

700
00:33:28,060 --> 00:33:29,820
- Just let him sing.
- He's a good singer.

701
00:33:29,820 --> 00:33:31,020
- Just listen to him.
- Sing.

702
00:33:31,020 --> 00:33:31,970
Sing.

703
00:33:32,370 --> 00:33:33,380
Impress me.

704
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:41,260
♪Stars are twinkling in the night sky♪

705
00:33:41,580 --> 00:33:43,200
Louder, louder.

706
00:33:43,490 --> 00:33:44,900
That's why

707
00:33:44,900 --> 00:33:46,180
they got you wrong.

708
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:48,090
Will Huang Han see me differently

709
00:33:48,100 --> 00:33:49,020
just because I'm tone-deaf?

710
00:33:49,660 --> 00:33:50,820
Use vocal resonance.

711
00:33:50,820 --> 00:33:54,420
♪Converging into the distant galaxy♪

712
00:33:54,420 --> 00:33:55,260
Yes.

713
00:33:55,260 --> 00:33:59,100
♪Dreams are shining ahead of us♪

714
00:33:59,300 --> 00:34:02,340
♪Shining ahead of us♪

715
00:34:02,340 --> 00:34:04,500
♪Just like the stars in the night sky♪

716
00:34:04,500 --> 00:34:07,600
♪Dreams are docked in the distance♪

717
00:34:07,760 --> 00:34:11,540
♪Just like the stars in the night sky♪

718
00:34:11,820 --> 00:34:14,940
♪The dreams in my heart are calling me♪

719
00:34:15,140 --> 00:34:19,130
♪I am unwilling to hide in the corner♪

720
00:34:19,290 --> 00:34:20,970
♪Keep it up, young man♪

721
00:34:20,970 --> 00:34:23,010
♪A youth like the wind♪

722
00:34:23,010 --> 00:34:26,730
♪Make your own future shine brighter♪

723
00:34:26,730 --> 00:34:28,350
♪Keep it up, young man♪

724
00:34:28,350 --> 00:34:30,420
♪Stand at a higher starting point♪

725
00:34:30,420 --> 00:34:34,130
♪Can't lose at the starting line♪

726
00:34:34,130 --> 00:34:35,730
♪Keep it up, young man♪

727
00:34:35,730 --> 00:34:37,810
♪Cross the finish line♪

728
00:34:37,810 --> 00:34:41,490
♪Applause and cheers are waiting for you♪

729
00:34:41,490 --> 00:34:43,120
♪Keep it up, young man♪

730
00:34:43,120 --> 00:34:45,090
♪Stay true to your beliefs♪

731
00:34:45,160 --> 00:34:46,000
Bravo!

732
00:34:46,580 --> 00:34:47,940
- Great!
- That was great!

733
00:34:47,940 --> 00:34:49,220
I admire you so much.

734
00:34:49,220 --> 00:34:50,780
Nie, I'm your biggest fan.

735
00:34:51,740 --> 00:34:52,940
Nie Chi, well done.

736
00:34:52,940 --> 00:34:53,780
- That was great.
- Exactly.

737
00:34:54,020 --> 00:34:55,020
How was it?

738
00:34:55,100 --> 00:34:56,420
You're not a good singer

739
00:34:56,540 --> 00:34:57,740
but a good person.

740
00:34:58,140 --> 00:34:59,460
See? I told you.

741
00:34:59,540 --> 00:35:00,380
Yes.

742
00:35:00,380 --> 00:35:02,180
Han, what about the promise?

743
00:35:03,940 --> 00:35:05,140
Oh, well...

744
00:35:05,980 --> 00:35:08,060
Nie Chi, I want to apologize to you

745
00:35:09,100 --> 00:35:10,180
in front of everyone.

746
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:12,980
I shouldn't have given you a hard time.

747
00:35:13,500 --> 00:35:14,340
I'm sorry.

748
00:35:19,100 --> 00:35:20,620
It's okay. I made a mistake too.

749
00:35:21,940 --> 00:35:23,140
Well, our coach said

750
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:25,580
we need to cooperate with each other.

751
00:35:25,580 --> 00:35:26,420
I've realized

752
00:35:26,420 --> 00:35:28,020
you're a nerd.

753
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:29,500
But it doesn't matter.

754
00:35:29,500 --> 00:35:30,420
I'll have your back.

755
00:35:30,940 --> 00:35:31,780
Thank you.

756
00:35:32,530 --> 00:35:33,430
That's great.

757
00:35:34,220 --> 00:35:35,220
Let's continue.

758
00:35:35,300 --> 00:35:36,470
Let me lose.

759
00:35:36,580 --> 00:35:37,780
