760
00:35:39,210 --> 00:35:40,060
- Come on.
- Okay.

761
00:35:40,060 --> 00:35:41,980
Rock, paper, scissors.

762
00:35:42,820 --> 00:35:44,580
Hurry, I took him down.

763
00:35:44,580 --> 00:35:45,420
Hurry.

764
00:35:45,620 --> 00:35:47,060
- Is this necessary?
- Of course.

765
00:35:47,060 --> 00:35:48,180
You're like strangers.

766
00:35:48,190 --> 00:35:49,030
Take a photo to show

767
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:50,220
