768
00:35:50,220 --> 00:35:51,780
Come on. Let's take a photo.

769
00:35:51,780 --> 00:35:52,940
- We're friends now.
- Come on.

770
00:35:52,940 --> 00:35:55,060
- Hong, take a photo for us.
- Okay. Come on.

771
00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:57,490
Three, two, one.

772
00:36:17,780 --> 00:36:18,620
Look good?

773
00:36:20,370 --> 00:36:21,210
Yes.

774
00:36:23,410 --> 00:36:24,320
Do you like it?

775
00:36:26,580 --> 00:36:27,420
Yes.

776
00:36:28,580 --> 00:36:29,640
Me too.

777
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:45,140
(Songbei Provincial Ice Sports Base)

778
00:36:45,140 --> 00:36:46,060
I need to think about

779
00:36:46,060 --> 00:36:47,460
the arrangement of the women's team.

780
00:36:47,660 --> 00:36:49,540
Let's follow the training schedule
for now.

781
00:36:50,420 --> 00:36:51,260
Coach.

782
00:36:51,620 --> 00:36:53,500
Who will help Lin Ge with the traction?

783
00:36:57,100 --> 00:36:58,620
Lin Feng, step forward.

784
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:01,300
Hurry.

785
00:37:06,860 --> 00:37:09,580
You'll do basic training with Lin Ge,

786
00:37:09,580 --> 00:37:11,380
