787
00:37:13,260 --> 00:37:16,780
Coach, I have good foundations.

788
00:37:18,140 --> 00:37:20,020
You were good when you just came here.

789
00:37:20,660 --> 00:37:22,300
However, everyone else has made progress

790
00:37:22,300 --> 00:37:23,460
