in a turn?

792
00:37:26,100 --> 00:37:27,780
Can you master narrow stride?

793
00:37:28,100 --> 00:37:29,100
Don't want to practice?

794
00:37:29,140 --> 00:37:30,700
Fine. You can go home.

795
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:35,500
Girls, let's start training.

796
00:37:36,100 --> 00:37:36,940
Hurry up.

797
00:37:37,180 --> 00:37:38,980
Boys, let's go to the ice rink.

798
00:37:42,980 --> 00:37:44,100
What are you waiting for?

799
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:19,810
♪Tears in my heart♪

800
00:38:20,170 --> 00:38:23,450
♪I've moved on♪

801
00:38:23,450 --> 00:38:27,320
♪I'm sad and restless♪

802
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:30,400
♪But I forgive you♪

803
00:38:30,680 --> 00:38:33,760
♪I shouldn't have been obsessed with you♪

804
00:38:34,160 --> 00:38:37,190
♪Should I leave or stay♪

805
00:38:37,300 --> 00:38:41,150
♪I can give up my dignity♪

806
